actions.message:
```                     
*Help             Lists available commands
*server           Shows info about a server    
*channe           Shows info about a channel
*user             Shows info about a User 
*OG               Send a The๛Originals Logo PNG
*timer            Set a Timer for a specific time
*mute             Mute a member from text channels 
*unmute           Unmutes a member
*kick             Kicks a member
*warn             Warn a member
*na7o             Bans a member
*ban              Bans a member
*giverole         give role to specific member
*clear            Cleans messages from a channel
*members          Shows Number of members in Serever
*inrole           Shows list of member in role
*dash             remove dash in specific text channel
*dashloop         remove dash in all text channels         
```
